<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Weißenburg</head><p>Der Rat bestätigt die für kommenden Sonntag erbetene Entsendung zweier Ratsherren nach Freystadt mit.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_149" id="74r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_149_r2l13"><expan>VVeiſſemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_149_r2l14"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan> Als Jr vns <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd <expan>gebete<ex>n</ex></expan> habt v̈mb cʒwen vnſers Rats </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_149_r2l15">daʒ vvir die cʒu <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>freunde<ex>n</ex></expan> auf den nehſten Suntag cʒu der freyenſtat </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_149_r2l16"><expan>ſchicke<ex>n</ex></expan> vvöllen / daſſelb vvir alſo <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> tun <expan>vvölle<ex>n</ex></expan> / <expan>vvan<ex>n</ex></expan> vvo vvir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erſ<ex>amkeit</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_149_r2l17">lieb vnd <expan>fr<ex>euntschaft</ex></expan> <expan>bevveiſe<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>möhte<ex>n</ex></expan> das <expan>tete<ex>n</ex></expan> vvir <expan>allcʒ<ex>eit</ex></expan> <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Auch vver eʒ daʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_149_r2l18">der tag niht für ſıch geen vvürde das lieſʒt vns 
<del rend="strikethrough">vviſſen </del> gutcʒeit vviſſen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_149_r2l19">daʒ dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> iht v̈mb ſüſt reẏten <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_149" id="74r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Weissemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>Fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, als ir uns
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und
                                <expan>gebete<ex>n</ex></expan> habt ümb czwen unsers rats, daz wir
                        die czu <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>freunde<ex>n</ex></expan> auf den nehsten suntag czu der Freyenstat
                                <expan>schicke<ex>n</ex></expan> wöllen, dasselb wir also
                                <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> tun <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan>,
                                <expan>wan<ex>n</ex></expan> wo wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ers<ex>amkeit</ex></expan> lieb und
                            <expan>fr<ex>euntschaft</ex></expan>
<expan>beweise<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>möhte<ex>n</ex></expan>, das <expan>tete<ex>n</ex></expan> wir
                                <expan>allcz<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>. Auch wer ez, daz der tag niht für sich geen
                        würde, das lieszt uns gutczeit wissen, daz die
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> iht ümb süst reyten.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
